rows.label: qst703302_msg0001
rows.name:
Oho, it's you lot. Thank you
for meeting me here.

rows.label: qst703302_msg0002
rows.name:
Let's get right to business. You see
that blighter over there?

rows.label: qst703302_msg0003
rows.name:
There was a little bother and
it's got me rather pinned down,
I'm afraid.

rows.label: qst703302_msg0004
rows.name:
Would you possibly be able to
clear it away for me?

rows.label: qst703302_msg0006
rows.name:
Do you think I'd be asking you
if I could do it myself?

rows.label: qst703302_msg0007
rows.name: It doesn't look that tough, though.

rows.label: qst703302_msg0008
rows.name:
I get the feeling that there's more
to this than you're letting on.

rows.label: qst703302_msg0010
rows.name: It's OK, Nuncle. We'll take care of it.

rows.label: qst703302_msg0011
rows.name:
Thank you! You're very kind to
an old Divine Beast.

rows.label: qst703302_msg0013
rows.name:
We'll handle it in a jiffy.
Consider it a favor.
